WEBVTT

00:06:56.565 --> 00:07:00.276
that could have made her
be accepted into the community --

00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:01.847
a baby boy,

00:07:01.871 --> 00:07:03.451
my baby brother.

00:07:04.731 --> 00:07:06.718
But he, too,

00:07:06.742 --> 00:07:09.354
joined the list of the dead.

00:07:11.982 --> 00:07:13.891
The most hurting part for me

00:07:15.409 --> 00:07:19.349
was the fact that I wasn't able
to attend my mother's burial.

00:07:19.984 --> 00:07:21.270
I wasn't allowed.

00:07:22.654 --> 00:07:27.354
They said her family did not find it fit

00:07:27.378 --> 00:07:31.162
for her children, who are all girls,
to attend her burial,